title: 3DSimed_2.0_29daysTrial.zip
description:
3DSimEd 2.0 is a visual tool allowing you to import data from many different formats including all Papyrus sims GTR2, rFactor, GTL, GTR, F1CC, Nascar SimRacing, Toca Race Driver, Nascar Heat, Viper Racing and many other sim formats.
A range of simple editing tools are available to allow you to modify data.
Your models can then be saved to GTR2, rFactor, GTL,  N2003,  GTR, Nascar Heat, Viper Racing and F1CC/F1-2002  formats.
3DSimEd also allows you to work with .3DS files giving a way for you to work with many 3D modelling applications.

29 Days Trial but without limitations
